            <li><strong>For direct bookings</strong> (your own website, repeat guests), you must collect and remit MAT yourself.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 id="deductible-expenses">Deductible Expenses: Lowering Your Tax Bill</h2>
          <p>This is where smart hosting pays off. The CRA allows you to deduct reasonable expenses incurred to earn your Airbnb income. The more you track, the less you owe. Here's what qualifies.</p>

