          <h3>Understanding "Partial" Deductions</h3>
          <p>Expenses like utilities, mortgage interest, and property tax must be <strong>pro-rated</strong> based on how much of your home is used for Airbnb and for how many days. The CRA expects a reasonable calculation. For example:</p>

